<div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none">
<blockquote>
<p><em>（挥手手）</em>嘿呀嘿呀，这里是<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">你啃不动的</span><strong><span style="color: blue">钻苹果</span></strong>，很高兴认识各位(*^▽^*)—<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/diamond-apple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190582); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5190582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Diamond_Apple" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5190582)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/diamond-apple" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5190582); return false;">Diamond_Apple</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>草你这个页面标题……出来吧，埃夫特！（大雾）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirius-dawn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5934437); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5934437&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Sirius Dawn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5934437)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirius-dawn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5934437); return false;">Sirius Dawn</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>恭喜。——<span class="error-inline"><em>LeonTeflon</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>？呼唤我？懂了，苹果，来做吧（肯定）。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><tt><em>人生最大的悲哀莫过于，你以为你在别人人事里是个狠人物，结果是个吃货 ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maybe-abs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5540157); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5540157&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Maybe-ABS" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5540157)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maybe-abs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5540157); return false;">Maybe-ABS</a></span></em></tt></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>留个言，别人的人事真有意思。――<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4423816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Dr_Naxurt" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4423816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-naxurt" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4423816); return false;">Dr_Naxurt</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>8说了，不愧是苹果。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5992128); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5992128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Swred" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5992128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swred" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5992128); return false;">Swred</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>事钻苹果，爱了（ ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5375092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="RainTree" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5375092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;">RainTree</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>钻苹果，噗嗤，整个人事都好好玩哈哈哈哈——路过的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>别人的人事真有意思，再回头看看自己的都是些什么鬼东西&#8230;&#8230;——ID和头像都很应景的过路人<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpasserby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5150580); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5150580&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="MrPasserby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5150580)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mrpasserby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5150580); return false;">MrPasserby</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>唔，不知道说啥的我，只是想来蹭个人事页，真的很有意思。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krampus-of-error" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6050311); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6050311&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Krampus of Error" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6050311)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/krampus-of-error" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6050311); return false;">Krampus of Error</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>有一说一，钻苹果蛮不错的（蹭人事）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lowpresence" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6139265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6139265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="LowPresence" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6139265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lowpresence" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6139265); return false;">LowPresence</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>金闪闪的&#8230;钻石苹果！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jane-rochester" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4291882); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4291882&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Jane Rochester" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4291882)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jane-rochester" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4291882); return false;">Jane Rochester</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>怎么合成（雾——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;">Frozen starry sky</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>啊，膜拜大佬（蹭人事——路过的鸽子<span class="error-inline"><em>pigeonLiu</em> 不匹配任何一个现有的用户名</span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>论如何杀人分尸一名SCP写手并将其食用？手把手教你，清洗……去皮……食用……娘的我牙也崩了。<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6119968&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="PiracyEssayist Zero" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6119968)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;">PiracyEssayist Zero</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>啊啊啊啊啊啊，谁想得到写出那么细思极恐的文的人人事页居然这么<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">沙雕</span>！我要啃个钻苹果平复一下心情——牙被崩掉前15秒的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xian-yu-bo-shi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6432694); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6432694&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Xian Yu Bo Shi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6432694)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xian-yu-bo-shi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6432694); return false;">Xian Yu Bo Shi</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>我永远喜欢钻钻——（ ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morphie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5001379); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5001379&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Morphie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5001379)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/morphie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5001379); return false;">Morphie</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>啊啊啊啊是可爱的钻果酱！！！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coffee-2020" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6751970); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6751970&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Coffee_2020" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6751970)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coffee-2020" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6751970); return false;">Coffee_2020</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>楼上的，果酱分我点。果子啃不动，果酱应该阔以……——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6591621&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="Confucian Lee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6591621)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/confucian-lee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6591621); return false;">Confucian Lee</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>果果我好喜欢你啊！我要为你电[数据删除]！！！！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4761754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="H-Storm Z" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4761754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/h-storm-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4761754); return false;">H-Storm Z</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p>据说当年树神埃夫特扎根于天狼星之上，用根须常年汲取着天狼星的能量。而天狼星每天都在燃烧分解着埃夫特的根，而那些树藤碳化之后脱离主干进入天狼星内核，在高温、高压下产生了一颗球形的钻石……<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6119968&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200850" alt="PiracyEssayist Zero" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6119968)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/piracyessayist-zero" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6119968); return false;">PiracyEssayist Zero</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
